item.title: I cant get my server on status list help!
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“x thiever x, post:3, topic:546483”]that the server is offline

(is offline, it must be online before you can register it here.)

What did I do wrong?[/quote]
It could be a bunch of things.
Check your firewall.
Check your portforwarding settings (in case your computer’s LAN IP has changed)
Make sure when you check on http://canyouseeme.org it says it can see you.
Make sure the server is indeed online when registering.
